{"tid":334395,"cid":13,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇減肥成功唔反彈嘅巴絲入嚟","createTime":"2017-07-24T15:43:59.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-05T11:16:35.000Z","uid":130032,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"ddc791621278d8a32102c8b3580593ee68e8e100","tid":334395,"uid":130032,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-24T15:43:59.000Z","msg":"八年前因為ex嫌我肥飛撚咗我，所以開始減肥<br />\n開頭兩個月一路keep住每日剩係食一碗菜同只飲一包果汁，其餘時間只係飲水，日日玩一個鐘籃球機，一個暑假減左5kg<br />\n<br />\n之後兩年都日日keep住做半個鐘運動同按摩比較鬆弛嘅身體部位等啲肉firm啲，每日早餐食半碗coco crunch加脫脂奶，午餐同下午剩係食青提子，5點後唔食野，其間係有食減肥藥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 副作用勁多，諗起都覺得辛苦，依家叫我再食我真係會頂唔順！<br />\n<br />\n其實減肥餐食咗兩年就開始變到好極端，第三年開始係咁買朱古力同成日食任食打邊爐，但係每次瘋狂食完都好內疚即刻衝去廁所嘔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 而我本身係骨架大，減左兩年由6x kg減到得返50kg都算成功，不過身體狀況亦都開始變差，所以諗住唔再減正常食返野，之後一年係食咩都唔吸收<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 依家咩都無做飲食又正常返慢慢反彈到同之前差唔多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好想減返肥，但係之前減得好辛苦，依家人又老驚身體承受唔住<br />\n<br />\n有冇巴絲係減肥一路keep住唔反彈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n利申 高164"},{"pid":"7487938893e521328fc02a50a4353a1b7dcac5fa","tid":334395,"uid":656,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-24T15:51:06.000Z","msg":"你呢種咁非人生活咁減梗係唔會堅持到"},{"pid":"62b478f402ddbf574bbbbe9f613608d368493b71","tid":334395,"uid":4660,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-24T15:54:02.000Z","msg":"恭喜，你好有可能有厭食症<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bfe55d0bd9c17029247cbe382ffb6ba4f29b7fbc","tid":334395,"uid":21423,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-24T15:55:00.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"7fbc670ef6c676b64b6b272412c15bc78004882e","tid":334395,"uid":73848,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-24T15:55:37.000Z","msg":"減肥減到咁撚on9"},{"pid":"e7bc8d35ae153d53d291abce1ead086f3869c82b","tid":334395,"uid":130032,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-24T15:56:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你呢種咁非人生活咁減梗係唔會堅持到</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n依家諗起都覺得自己個陣好痴線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔知點解仲可以堅持到兩年非人生活<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3559da50c71f718bef9f401eb672dabb99c188f0","tid":334395,"uid":130032,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-24T15:57:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>恭喜，你好有可能有厭食症<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n依家正常返，但係都肥返<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"80c265c364156bf190550009322690b5ebe61e64","tid":334395,"uid":130032,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-24T16:00:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>164cm減完都冇人要啦<br />\n除非做0仔</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔記得利申我係絲 <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d81dd16e73f0eded266c32203e69366962f876c","tid":334395,"uid":60042,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-24T16:03:00.000Z","msg":"8x 減到而家70到 之後一直落唔到去 算唔算 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab8b92b26beb8f12484d868dd4bef98668079129","tid":334395,"uid":130032,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-24T16:03:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>減肥減到咁撚on9</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n依家諗返都覺得好on9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n個陣失戀太大打擊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 依家冇野打擊我即刻肥返<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n要著返以前啲肥婆衫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"599e5faed038da898b5c229b0d8b81bd7a6eda52","tid":334395,"uid":35043,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-24T16:05:24.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5d69e4ba9ace5c43ae4ad79816dc7ddb97586968","tid":334395,"uid":35043,"lik