,"tid":334395,"uid":128277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-24T16:15:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"286485495e6a0b009fb44392ead586cbc8b87fa9","tid":334395,"uid":128277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-24T16:17:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6603e378c6d266a3813e19257f917195f946053f","tid":334395,"uid":73369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-24T16:20:07.000Z","msg":"由90kg減到最輕75，不過無耐又上番80<br />\n依家keep住左80落唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a1a0cc6b3fa81aa996f8e203bddf53b93d4c2b9","tid":334395,"uid":120854,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-24T16:20:47.000Z","msg":"我"},{"pid":"d3fd732803ce4e1d12bb6efaff93de1e62265b04","tid":334395,"uid":60042,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-24T16:38:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>8x 減到而家70到 之後一直落唔到去 算唔算 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n巴打減左幾耐？減左1x kg都算係咁，我都係50就落唔到，如果唔係減到身體變差我都會繼續減<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n半年到 之前去台灣踩左個環島翻黎 體重冇變 不過體脂就跌左幾%<br />\n之後係換左份要體力勞動既工  食早餐同夜晚 中午飯唔食 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n食野同之前一樣 冇介口 咩都食 食到飽 <br />\n同埋都冇運動 <br />\n<br />\n不過可能因為冇運動 所以而家keep住70落唔到 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"01394874b3110f821589b02c93a1f12d944fd676","tid":334395,"uid":119783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-24T16:41:05.000Z","msg":"食朱古力同辣野 中午早餐食多啲"},{"pid":"868da741a4593e09287387f5cf2c2734db32c4fd","tid":334395,"uid":123713,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-24T16:45:45.000Z","msg":"1.唔好單純追求體重 諗清楚你追求緊既係健康（e.g. Body fat) 定線條<br />\n<br />\n2.節食減肥注定會反彈 除左你下半世都唔會正常食返野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n身體入面既瘦素一直控制你食完野吸收幾多（肥既元凶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ）你食少左野 身體會減少瘦素黎比你吸收多d (生物本能） <br />\n你一正常食返 自然反彈"},{"pid":"c88a01910bcb28faf61606c6f3a72cf34fd25355","tid":334395,"uid":38580,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-24T16:57:11.000Z","msg":"我覺得只靠節食冇咩用 一定反彈，因為好多時同人地出去食都忍唔到口<br />\n所以一定要做運動，如果你體重有番咁上下 可以去跑步游水跳舞 減得快d<br />\n減到咁上下磅數就做番修線條運動 例如yoga<br />\n仲要靠飲食 先要戒甜戒凍嘢<br />\n早午晚3餐一定要食足<br />\n我係早午餐咩都食，但都會少油少鹽少糖<br />\n但晚餐盡量8點前食 食一碗麥皮加一至2個奇異果<br />\n有恒心一定瘦<br />\nP.s.之前咁樣瘦左10磅 又可以著bikini 去左旅行食多左嘢冇運動 都唔會肥 當然去完旅行都要飲食同運動就要回復番正常"},{"pid":"f1f395e07b3b51d17850322e25cf35dc3d7cd9ca","tid":334395,"uid":28792,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-24T17:10:38.000Z","msg":"做運動啦"}]}